name: Maps
description:
New EP from The Ruby Kid, produced by Dan Angell, featuring guest production from Keybored, Core-B and Hash Finger.

1 - All Hands On Deck
2 - The Key
3 - Hoxton Bounce
4 - Growing Up Is A Euphemism For Knowing Your Place (feat. Al Baker)
5 - Morning-After Snow
6 - Maps (feat. Paula Chalmers)
7 - Ends/Means
8 - Poems of Place I: The Unreal City
9 - Poems of Place II: The Imagined Village (with Black Jacobins, live in session for BBC Radio Sheffield - July 2009)

www.therubykid.com

name: Winter In The City
description:
The Ruby Kid's 6-track EP, released in March 2009, features his backing band Black Jacobins and includes the following tracks:

1 - Art Versus Industry
2 - Winter In The City
3 - A La Recherche...
4 - East 6th St. (Between 2nd & 3rd)
5 - March 25th, 1911
6 - Labor's Giant Step

http://www.myspace.com/therubykid

name: Official Red Scare Tour poster

Exclusively designed by Ross 'Appeal' Bownes of Appealing Design (http://www.appealingdesign.co.uk).
